<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="A1">
<sup>1</sup>Rega Institute, Katholieke Universiteit Leuven, Leuven, Belgium</div>
<div id="A2">
<sup>2</sup>Departments of Biomathematics and Human Genetics, David Geffen School of Medicine; Department of Biostatistics, School of Public Health; University of California, Los Angeles, United States</div>
<div id="A3">
<sup>3</sup>Centro de Malária e outras Doenças Tropicais, Instituto de Higiene e Medicina Tropical, Lisboa, Portugal</div>
<div id="A4">
