<li id="R4">
<span class="label">4.</span><cite>Sharp PM, Hahn BH. AIDS: prehistory of HIV-1. Nature. 2008;455:605–606. doi: 10.1038/455605a.</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/455605a" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18833267/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Nature&amp;title=AIDS:%20prehistory%20of%20HIV-1&amp;author=PM%20Sharp&amp;author=BH%20Hahn&amp;volume=455&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;pages=605-606&amp;pmid=18833267&amp;doi=10.1038/455605a&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R5">
